<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>500 – Internal Server Error | Rixi Lab</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/img/Rixi Lab New Logo PNG.png" rel="icon" />
  <link href="/img/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:        #040000;
      --surface:   #191919;
      --text:      #f8f8f8;
      --muted:     rgba(248,248,248,0.55);
      --accent:    #ff6600;
      --accent-glow: rgba(255,102,0,0.18);
      --danger:    #ff3333;
      --danger-glow: rgba(255,51,51,0.15);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      width: 540px; height: 540px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--danger-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      top: -18%; right: -10%;
      animation: drift 7s ease-in-out infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      width: 300px; height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      bottom: 5%; left: 3%;
      animation: drift 5s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    @keyframes drift {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-22px); }
    }

    .grid-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,102,0,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,102,0,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 22px 48px;
      background: rgba(4,0,0,0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-brand {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .nav-brand img {
      height: 32px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .nav-brand span { color: var(--accent); }
    nav a.nav-link {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.25s;
    }
    nav a.nav-link:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; }

    main {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .error-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,51,51,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,51,51,0.35);
      border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--danger);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .badge-dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      background: var(--danger);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100% { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
      50% { opacity:0.3; transform:scale(0.65); }
    }

    .error-code {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(120px, 22vw, 260px);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 20%, var(--danger) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      position: relative;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .error-code::before,
    .error-code::after {
      content: attr(data-text);
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 20%, var(--danger) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .error-code::before {
      animation: glitch1 3s infinite;
      clip-path: polygon(0 25%, 100% 25%, 100% 42%, 0 42%);
      transform: translateX(-3px);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    .error-code::after {
      animation: glitch2 3.8s infinite;
      clip-path: polygon(0 58%, 100% 58%, 100% 72%, 0 72%);
      transform: translateX(3px);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    @keyframes glitch1 {
      0%,88%,100% { transform:translateX(0); opacity:0; }
      90% { transform:translateX(-5px); opacity:0.7; }
      93% { transform:translateX(4px); opacity:0.5; }
    }
    @keyframes glitch2 {
      0%,85%,100% { transform:translateX(0); opacity:0; }
      87% { transform:translateX(5px); opacity:0.5; }
      91% { transform:translateX(-4px); opacity:0.4; }
    }

    .error-divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 8px 0 24px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
    }
    .error-divider::before,
    .error-divider::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,51,51,0.45), transparent);
    }
    .error-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; }

    .error-title {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .error-desc {
      font-size: 0.97rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 420px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    /* Terminal-style detail block */
    .terminal-block {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,51,51,0.2);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--danger);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 100%;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .terminal-block .t-label { color: var(--danger); font-weight: bold; }

    .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
    .btn {
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 13px 32px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(255,102,0,0.35);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 36px rgba(255,102,0,0.55);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 18px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      background: rgba(4,0,0,0.5);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav { padding: 18px 24px; }
      .nav-links { gap: 20px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 420px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .btn-group { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      .btn { width: 100%; max-width: 280px; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="grid-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-brand"><img src="/img/Rixi Lab New Logo PNG.png" alt="Rixi Lab Logo">Rixi <span>Lab</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
      <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <div class="error-badge">
      <span class="badge-dot"></span>
      Critical Error
    </div>

    <div class="error-code" data-text="500" aria-label="500">500</div>

    <div class="error-divider">
      <span class="error-icon">⚡</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="error-title">Internal Server Error</h1>
    <p class="error-desc">
      Something went wrong on our end. Our servers encountered an unexpected condition and couldn't complete your request.
    </p>

    <div class="terminal-block">
      <div><span class="t-label">STATUS</span>  500 Internal Server Error</div>
      <div><span class="t-label">CODE</span>    INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR</div>
      <div><span class="t-label">INFO</span>    Server-side exception encountered</div>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Go Home</a>
      <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="btn btn-secondary">Try Again</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2026 Rixi Lab &nbsp;·&nbsp; HTTP 500 Internal Server Error
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
